    <name>Elementary Intelligence</name>
    <summary>Summon any AI chat service from a system-wide shortcut</summary>
    <description>
        <p>
            Elementary Intelligence runs quietly in the background. Press a
            system-wide shortcut to bring up a simple entry, type your message,
            and it opens your chosen AI assistant with the message ready to send.
        </p>
        <p>
            Pick your service — Claude, ChatGPT, Gemini or Mistral — and your
            trigger combination from a small, native settings window.
        </p>
    </description>

    <developer id="com.github.breitburg">
        <name>breitburg</name>
    </developer>

